---
import EshopShell from './_components/EshopShell.astro';
---

<EshopShell
  title="About VaultMart"
  activePage="about"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'VaultMart', href: '/l1/eshop/' },
    { label: 'About' },
  ]}
>

  <div class="pageTitle">About VaultMart</div>

  <div style="margin: 0 15px;">

    <div class="infoBox" style="margin: 10px 0;">
      <strong>VaultMart</strong> &mdash; Your Source for Dwarven Goods &amp; Surface Imports<br>
      A Division of Koganusan Estates LLC &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; Founded Year 298 &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; Z-Level 3, Mountainhome Commercial District
    </div>

    <!-- Company History -->
    <h2>Company History</h2>
    <p>
      VaultMart was founded in Year 298 by the Koganusan Estates LLC commercial division as a
      centralised procurement platform for Mountainhome residents and surrounding z-level settlements.
      Beginning as a single-counter stall on Z-Level 3, VaultMart expanded to its current catalogue
      of 28 product lines spanning five categories.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our growth tracked the expansion of the Mountainhome fortress itself: as new z-levels opened
      and the population grew, demand for standardised goods — mining equipment, forge supplies,
      foodstuffs, furniture, and surface-traded materials — required a reliable fulfilment operation.
      Today, VaultMart serves over 2,400 registered customer accounts across 14 z-levels.
    </p>

    <!-- Vendor Partners -->
    <h2>Vendor Partners</h2>
    <p>VaultMart sources products from a network of approved vendors operating under Bureau of Deep Works
    quality standards.</p>

    <table class="aspNetTable">
      <thead>
        <tr class="headerRow">
          <th>Vendor</th>
          <th>Category</th>
          <th>Notes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Dwarven Iron Guild</strong></td>
          <td>Mining &amp; Excavation; Forge &amp; Smithing</td>
          <td>Primary supplier for iron/steel ingots, certified tools, and mining equipment. Guild certification required for all Grade A products.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="alternatingRow">
          <td><strong>Mountainhome Ale Guild</strong></td>
          <td>Food &amp; Brewing</td>
          <td>Sole licensed brewer under Guild Charter Year 89. Supplies all ale and brewing products. See the <a href="/l1/news/">Mountainhome Herald</a> for current batch news.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Bureau of Subterranean Agriculture</strong></td>
          <td>Food &amp; Brewing</td>
          <td>Certifies plump helmet seeds and prepared food products. All food items carry BSA hygiene certification.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="alternatingRow">
          <td><strong>Fungiwood Trust</strong></td>
          <td>Food &amp; Brewing</td>
          <td>Exclusive supplier of Fungiwood Cavern Biome mushroom wines. Limited-vintage batches. Registry of Deeds property holder; see <a href="/l1/taxes/">ROD Records</a> (CLM-999-FUNGI).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Headshoots LLC</strong></td>
          <td>Mining &amp; Excavation (blasting)</td>
          <td>Licensed manufacturer of blasting charges and siege components. Note: Headshoots LLC is subject to ongoing civil proceedings regarding safety log compliance; all current stock meets Bureau standards. See the <a href="/l1/news/">Herald</a> for coverage.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="alternatingRow">
          <td><strong>Bureau of Surface Commerce</strong></td>
          <td>Surface Imports</td>
          <td>Authorises all surface-import goods. Trade route disruptions affect surface import availability. Current route advisory in effect through mid-season.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Human &amp; Elven Trade Partners</strong></td>
          <td>Surface Imports</td>
          <td>Various surface trade partners including the Elven Forest Trading Post and human Southern/Eastern Markets. Subject to route availability and diplomatic status.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- Shipping Policy -->
    <h2>Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy</h2>
    <p>All in-stock items are dispatched from our Z-Level 3 warehouse within one working day of order
    confirmation. Standard delivery rates apply:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Z-Levels 1–5: Next day, included in order price</li>
      <li>Z-Levels 6–30: 1–2 working days, 2.00 GS flat fee</li>
      <li>Z-Levels 31–80: 2–4 working days, 3.50 GS flat fee</li>
      <li>Z-Levels 81+: 4–7 working days, 5.00 GS flat fee</li>
      <li>Surface delivery: Subject to route availability; additional charges apply</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <strong>Current Advisory:</strong> Surface imports (including Elven Cloth, Surface Lumber,
      and Human Spice Packs) may be delayed due to blizzard conditions and goblin raiding on the
      primary surface trade route. The Bureau of Surface Commerce expects restoration by mid-season.
    </p>

    <!-- Returns Policy -->
    <h2>Returns &amp; Warranty</h2>
    <p>VaultMart accepts returns on most items within 14 days of delivery, subject to the following
    conditions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Items must be unused and in original packaging</li>
      <li>Blasting charges and prepared food items are non-returnable once custody transferred</li>
      <li>Ingot bundles subject to Bureau of Deep Works weight inspection before credit issued</li>
      <li>Surface imports subject to a 20% restocking fee due to limited supply</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Warranty terms follow Guild and Bureau standards as noted on each product listing.</p>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <table class="formTable" style="width:auto; margin:0;">
      <tr><td class="labelCol"><strong>Address:</strong></td><td>VaultMart Warehouse, Z-Level 3, South Commercial Corridor, Mountainhome</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="labelCol"><strong>Dispatch Hours:</strong></td><td>1st Bell to 6th Bell, all days</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="labelCol"><strong>Customer Service:</strong></td><td>vaultmart-cs@koganusan-estates.mh</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="labelCol"><strong>Corporate:</strong></td><td>Koganusan Estates LLC, Z-Level 55, Deep Sector &mdash; <a href="/l1/taxes/">ROD Records: CLM-304-KOGAN</a></td></tr>
    </table>

  </div>

</EshopShell>
